cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper deals with the problem of user association in small cell networks, which is a topic related to network protocols and algorithms in wireless communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a matching game model and a distributed algorithm to solve it, which are related to game theory and optimization. Thus, cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are also possible categories. The paper also mentions fairness and utility distribution, which are related to control and system theory, so cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category. Finally, the paper includes simulation results, which may involve multimedia processing and analysis, so cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely but still possible category.
